Highlight wall panels have the property of reflecting light, making the walls appear bright and sparkling. This reflective property provides more possibilities for decorative effects. Utilizing the unique luster and texture of highlight wall panels, designers can visually extend the space, create a sense of spatial depth and grandeur, and make small spaces appear more spacious and open. It is used in luxury residences, commercial places, and hotels, it can add a sense of luxury and quality to it.
